author: Upper Echelon
description:
BitBoy is having another (perhaps his last) public meltdown, after years of becoming an internet spectacle. The once world famous crypto influencer is now embroiled in a legal battle, spinning tales of complex conspiracies, and openly attack the justice system presiding over him in a bizarre display of what can happen when Greed comes calling to collect your bill.

When building a fortune of ill-gotten gains, don't be surprised when someone comes to steal it from you. I hope he can figure it all out, and finally change himself for the better, but right now hes a cautionary tale about the dangers of shallow materialism.
